@startuml seq-20-admin-department-merge
title POST /admin/departments/merge

actor "Administrator" as A <<human>>
participant "Browser" as B <<browser>>
participant "Express\n/admin" as API <<service>>
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

B -> API: POST /admin/departments/merge\n{ sourceDepartmentId, targetDepartmentId }

API -> DB: load source + target departments
alt Same id / missing
  API --> B: 400 / 404
else OK
  API -> DB: $transaction
  note right
    Reassign **UserDepartmentAccess** with\nlevel merge rules; bump **authVersion**\nfor affected users; move users' primary\ndepartmentId; move documents' departmentId;\ndelete source department.
  end note
  alt Source has child departments
    API --> B: 409 Reassign children first
  else Success
    API --> B: 200 { ok, mergedInto }
  end
end

note right of API
  Source: **apps/api/src/routes/admin.ts** (~392+).
end note

@enduml
